---------------------------------------
- Summary
---------------------------------------

Helper script to setup and build a specific configuration of the Athena Game
Framework during development.

It's up to you to clone the appropriate GIT repositories in the dependencies/
folder and switch to the desired branches in order to setup the Athena Game
Framework the way you want it.


